ht at the Upper Deck with an ACG coupon 2 for 1 cheeseburger. These were very good &amp; huge portions. Bill was $13 + tip, very good price.Because of the inconvience of the ticket situation we did not gamble much here. But we would stay again if the price was right or better yet if we received some great offer. We did use the Deuce to go to the strip one day, and of course the VC is the whole length of Fremont Street away from the bus stop, so that was a bit of walking that we did not need.I would compare the VC to a Super 8 here in the Midwest, a budget hotel.	
